  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为AXI总线监控模块设计一个清晰的架构图。核心是基于axi_monitor_base的封装，里面要处理三种AXI通道的输入。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "axi_monitor_base",
        "CMD",
        "DATA",
        "RESP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，三种通道是指命令、数据和响应？我打算把这三个归到一个叫\"AXI Channel Inputs\"的分组里，这样视觉上比较紧凑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXI_Channels",
        "CMD",
        "DATA",
        "RESP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，命令通道管AR/AW，数据通道管R/W，响应通道专门处理B。这个分组名可以。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CMD",
        "DATA",
        "RESP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，AXI输入部分我先画好了。接下来内部结构怎么安排？axi_monitor_base里面需要哪些子模块？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "axi_monitor_base"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "内部我想到四个核心子系统：Transaction Manager负责事务追踪，Timeout Monitor做超时检测，Performance Tracker统计性能，还有一个Reporter统一输出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Trans_Mgr",
        "Timeout",
        "Perf",
        "Reporter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Transaction Manager里面是不是还需要细分？比如事务表和ID追踪逻辑？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Trans_Mgr",
        "TABLE",
        "TRACK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Transaction Table要支持MAX_TRANSACTIONS个条目，还要有基于ID的beat计数追踪。这两个可以放在Trans_Mgr的子层级。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Trans_Mgr",
        "TABLE",
        "TRACK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Trans_Mgr的子结构我加上了。Timeout Monitor那边，超时阈值是可配置的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Timeout",
        "TMO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，TMO要支持per-phase的超时检测，阈值通过配置寄存器来设。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Timeout",
        "TMO",
        "Config"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那我给Timeout下面放一个TMO节点，描述成\"Per-phase timeouts, Configurable thresholds\"。另外配置部分我打算单独拎出来成一个Config分组，包含cfg_*_enable这些寄存器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Config",
        "CFG",
        "Timeout",
        "TMO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，cfg_freq_sel频率选择也要放进去。配置要连到Timeout和Perf两个模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Config",
        "CFG",
        "Timeout",
        "Perf"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Config分组和连线我加上了。Performance Tracker那边，Latency measurement和Throughput metrics够吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Perf",
        "PERF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "够了，PERF节点就描述这两个功能。Reporter模块要处理packet格式化，还有一个事件队列。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Perf",
        "PERF",
        "Reporter",
        "PKT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Reporter下面加了PKT节点，描述\"Packet formatting, Event queuing\"。现在来看输出部分，monitor bus怎么定义？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reporter",
        "PKT",
        "MONBUS",
        "Output"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "输出做一个Monitor Bus Output分组，包含monbus_packet[63:0]数据总线和valid信号，再加一个STATUS端口输出busy和active_count状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Output",
        "MONBUS",
        "STATUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，MONBUS描述成\"monbus_packet[63:0], monbus_valid\"，STATUS加上\"busy, active_count, block_ready\"。现在理一下数据流：三个AXI通道都连到Trans_Mgr？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CMD",
        "DATA",
        "RESP",
        "Trans_Mgr",
        "MONBUS",
        "STATUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，CMD、DATA、RESP三条线都进Trans_Mgr。Trans_Mgr还要连到Timeout、Perf和Reporter。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CMD",
        "DATA",
        "RESP",
        "Trans_Mgr",
        "Timeout",
        "Perf",
        "Reporter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "这些连线我画上了。Config到Timeout和Perf的线也加上了。Reporter的输出连到MONBUS，这个没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reporter",
        "MONBUS",
        "Config",
        "Timeout",
        "Perf"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题。还有Trans_Mgr要直接输出STATUS状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Trans_Mgr",
        "STATUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "STATUS连线加上了。我检查一下：Timeout和Perf都要连到Reporter对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Timeout",
        "Perf",
        "Reporter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，超时事件和性能统计都要上报给Reporter统一打包。另外Trans_Mgr本身的事务完成信息也要给Reporter。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Timeout",
        "Perf",
        "Trans_Mgr",
        "Reporter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，Trans_Mgr到Reporter的线我也补上了。整体结构看起来差不多了，我过一遍分组命名：AXI_Channels、Config、axi_monitor_base、Output，这些OK吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXI_Channels",
        "Config",
        "axi_monitor_base",
        "Output"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "axi_monitor_base的分组名我觉得直接用模块名本身，但里面四个子系统要不要也考虑子分组的形式？比如Trans_Mgr里面TABLE和TRACK的层级关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "axi_monitor_base",
        "Trans_Mgr",
        "TABLE",
        "TRACK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已经做了，Trans_Mgr、Timeout、Perf、Reporter都是axi_monitor_base的子分组，TABLE和TRACK是Trans_Mgr的子节点。这样层级比较清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "axi_monitor_base",
        "Trans_Mgr",
        "Timeout",
        "Perf",
        "Reporter",
        "TABLE",
        "TRACK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 25,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有个细节，Config分组里的寄存器描述我想再精确一点：cfg_*_enable是开关，cfg_*_cnt是计数配置，cfg_freq_sel是时钟分频。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Config",
        "CFG"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 26,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "CFG节点的描述我更新为\"cfg_*_enable, cfg_*_cnt, cfg_freq_sel\"。这样配置项一目了然。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Config",
        "CFG"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 27,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Timeout和Perf之间有没有直接交互？还是都各自独立上报Reporter？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Timeout",
        "Perf",
        "Reporter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 28,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "目前设计是两者都独立连到Reporter，没有直接的Timeout到Perf的连线。需要加吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Timeout",
        "Perf",
        "Reporter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 29,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不需要，保持独立上报就行。但Trans_Mgr和Timeout之间要有交互，因为超时检测需要知道事务状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Trans_Mgr",
        "Timeout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 30,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已经有了，Trans_Mgr到Timeout的连线我确认存在。那Perf的数据来源也是Trans_Mgr？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Trans_Mgr",
        "Perf"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 31,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Trans_Mgr把事务时序信息给Perf做latency和throughput计算。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Trans_Mgr",
        "Perf"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 32,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，所有核心连线都确认完毕。我再看一下STATUS的输出，block_ready信号是什么场景用的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STATUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 33,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "block_ready表示监控器是否还能接受新事务，当active_count达到MAX_TRANSACTIONS时要拉低。",
