        "STATUS",
        "Trans_Mgr",
        "TABLE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 34,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，所以STATUS是Trans_Mgr根据TABLE状态生成的。整个图我基本画完了，再确认一下分组标题的显示方式：AXI Channel Inputs、Configuration、axi_monitor_base、Monitor Bus Output，这些显示文本没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXI_Channels",
        "Config",
        "axi_monitor_base",
        "Output"
